  m_Text: "Tis character use a LPSP rocket launcher which was copied to the character
    with editor scripts. Including related SkinnedMeshRenderers and all bone hierachies.\nThe
    bone Transforms are synchroinzed by FPSBoneSynchronizer.cs, and as the created
    weapon and bones are under character hierarchy, the baked animations will contain
    the weapon movement as well. \nThis is just a demonstration. You probably need
    your own workflow to re-use LPSP weapons. Depending on your need."
